# Kubernetes manifests

- Ingress: Gateway API (`Gateway` + `HTTPRoute`) via Cilium — no Istio VirtualServices.
- Observability namespace: `observability` (Prometheus, Grafana, Loki, Jaeger).
- Hubble UI exposed at `hubble.ederbrito.com.br`; no Kiali.
- TLS: cert-manager Certificate in `kube-system` (or gateway ns) + HTTP-01 via Cilium ingress class.
- Frontend namespace: `ederbrito` — no sidecar injection labels.
- Do not pin production image SHAs in Deployment YAML; CI runs `kubectl set image`.
- Keep resource requests/limits modest for Always Free (2× A1.Flex).
- Prefer fully qualified image names (registry/path:tag).
